洗衣日表示艾德·希兰的开幕“感觉不在我们的可能性范围内” https://www.nme.com/news/music/laundry-day-interview-ed-sheeran-new-york-opening-1975-matty-healy-drake-3757575?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=laundry-day-访谈-ed-sheeran-纽约-开幕-1975-马蒂-希利-德雷克Anagricel DuranWed, 22 May 2024 15:22:29 +0000 Music InterviewsMusic NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3757575 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洗衣日。图片来源：卡米拉·弗兰奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>纽约四人组已接受 NME 采访，破解 TikTok 算法，并由 Drake 和 Matty Healy 等人联合签名，并在 Bowery Ballroom 的两晚门票全部售完</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/laundry-day-interview-ed-sheeran-new-york-opening-1975-matty-healy-drake-3757575">《洗衣日》后称艾德·希兰的开场“感觉不在我们的可能性范围内”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="洗衣日。图片来源：卡米拉·弗兰奇" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Laundry-Day.-Credit-Camilla-Ffrench-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-cont